    "body": "This is a consequence of our v0.4 testnet, which our fork choice would be broken and would have two partitioned chains where a validator would be active in one chain but unknown in another, leading to `cannot verify bitfield` problems. This is a known bug that is resolved by latest changes to fork choice and our updates to the v0.8.1 specification as of latest master.",
